---
title: Spice Market Coconut Salmon with Green Beans, Bell Pepper & Cilantro Lime Rice
description: Cardamom, turmeric, fenugreek, cumin: the aromas of the spice market will waft through your kitchen with this quick-to-the-table meal. And when combined with fresh cilantro, lime, ginger, and coconut milk you’ll have the perfect richly flavored complement to roasted salmon. The dish is finished with tender bell pepper and green beans, then spooned over cilantro jasmine rice for soaking up every last drop.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spice-market-coconut-salmon-939276e2.jpg
